-- Medellin Wastewater Plant to Be Running by 2015, BNAmericas Says
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-07-09T09:58:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-09/medellin-wastewater-plant-to-be-running-by-2015-bnamericas-says.html
Empresas Publicas de Medellin ESP
plans to have the Bello sewage plant operating by September
2015, BNamericas reported, citing the state water utility’s head
of wastewater-treatment projects.  Work on the $347 million project to boost wastewater-treatment coverage in  Colombia ’s Medellin river basin to 95
percent by completion and reduce the dumping of effluent in the
river began in September 2012, EMP’s Carlos Enrique Munoz told
the publication.  To contact the reporter on this story:
